(When a user submits a task, this is the flow:) Tj
0 -15 Td
() Tj
0 -15 Td
(1. The frontend sends the task to `POST /api/tasks`.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(2. FastAPI creates a new `TaskRecord`.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(3. The task is stored in a local JSON-backed task store.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(4. A background task starts execution.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(5. The `supervisor` inspects the task and decides the task type.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(6. The supervisor chooses which specialist agent should run.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(7. The graph runner initializes the execution path.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(8. The specialist agent runs with a restricted tool/permission scope.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(9. The agent writes outputs into shared memory and traces.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(10. The `critic` reviews the specialist output.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(11. The supervisor merges all outputs into final sections and artifacts.) Tj
0 -15 Td
(12. The frontend polls the task and renders status, trace, memory, and final output.) Tj
0 -15 Td
() Tj
0 -15 Td
(4. TASK TYPES SUPPORTED) Tj
0 -15 Td
() Tj
ET
